  <thing id="io5CMgcFlc" name="Magic Fleece" description="This garment is made from the carefully-sheared fleece of a Nyx-fleece ram. Once attuned to and worn, it provides one of the following benefits:\n\n{b}Protection.{/b} You gain a +1 bonus to your AC and saving throws.\n{b}Power of Nyx.{/b} You have advantage on all Charisma (Persuasion) checks.\n{b}Calming Presence.{/b} You can cast {i}calm emotions{/i} once per day (with a save DC of 13).\n{b}Trail of Flowers.{/b} Wherever you walk, flowers sprout up magically behind you. They wilt away after 1 hour.\n{b}Animal Affinity.{/b} Unless you are evil, you can cast {i}animal friendship{/i} once per day (with a save DC of 13).\n{b}Abundance of Food.{/b} You can cast {i}create food and water{/i} once per day." compset="Wondrous">
