  <thing id="i5CKhrusor" name="Khrusor, Spear of Heliod" description="{b}Spear of the Sun{/b}. This spear grants a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with it. When you hit with an attack using this spear, the target takes an additional 2d8 radiant damage.\n\n{b}Blessing of the Sun{/b}Blessing of the Sun. If you aren&apos;t a worshiper of Heliod, the spear has 2 randomly determined major detrimental properties. If you are a worshiper of Heliod, you gain all the below piety benefits, so long as you have the piety required:\n{b}Piety 3+{/b}. You gain 15 temporary hit points each dawn.\n{b}Piety 10+{/b}. The spear has 1 randomly determined minor beneficial property.\n{b}Piety 25+{/b}. The spear has another randomly determined minor beneficial property.\n{b}Piety 50+{/b}. The spear has 1 randomly determined major beneficial property.\nSee the Artifacts section in chapter 7 of the DMG for more information on randomly determined properties. Use the Artifact Properties tab to select the properties, and associate each property with this artifact once selected.\n\n{b}Luminous{/b}. The spear sheds bright sunlight in a 30-foot radius and dim sunlight for another 30 feet.\n\n{b}Sun&apos;s Retaliation{/b}. When you suffer damage from a creature within 5 feet of you, you can take a reaction to make a melee attack with the spear against that creature. On a hit, the spear deals its normal damage, and the creature is blinded until the beginning of its next turn. This property of the spear can&apos;t be used again until the next dawn.\n\n{b}Spells{/b}. The spear has 10 charges, regaining 1d6+4 spent charges each dawn. While holding it, you can use an action to spend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of these spells (save DC 18) from it: guiding bolt (1 charge), daylight (3 charges, targeting the tip of the spear only), sunbeam (6 charges).\n\n\n{b}{i}Hero Lab Note{/i}{/b}. If your DM is allowing you to gain the Piety benefits of this weapon without worshipping its deity, add the &quot;Ignore Theros Artifact Restrictions&quot; adjustment to your character." compset="MagicWep">
