  <thing id="io5CPyxis" name="Pyxis of Pandemonium" description="A creature that touches this ornate wooden vessel for 1 minute gains the benefits of a short rest. That creature also gains the effects of the {i}bless{/i} spell until the creature completes a short or long rest. Once a creature has gained these benefits, it cannot do so again until it completes a long rest.\n\nIf the vessel is opened, roll a d8. The numbered effect below corresponding to the number rolled occurs. Any spells cast by the vessel have a spell save DC of 17. One minute after the vessel is opened, it disappears, then reappears, sealed, in a random location on the same plane of existence once 24 hours have passed.\n\n{b}Curse{/b}. Any creature that gains the short rest benefit from the vessel hears whispers in their mind, emanating from the vessel. That creature must make a DC 17 Wisdom save. On a failure, the creature is charmed by the vessel for 1 hour. The charmed creature does everything it can to open the vessel as soon as possible. On a successful save, the creature is immune to the vessel&apos;s whispers for 24 hours.\n\n{b}Calamity{/b}\n{b}1 - Androphagia{/b}. Each creature within 60 feet of the vessel must make a DC 17 Wisdom save, going berserk for 1 minute on a failure. A berserk creature must start its turn using the Attack action to make one melee or ranged attack (its choice) against the closest creature. The berserk creature can repeat the save at the end of its turn, ending the effect for itself on a success.\n{b}2 - Bile Blight{/b}. The vessel casts {i}harm{/i} on every creature within 30 feet of it.\n{b}3 - Flood{/b}. The vessel casts {i}tsunami{/i} at a point within 120 feet of it, chosen by the DM.\n{b}4 - Medusa&apos;s Gaze{/b}. The vessel casts {i}flesh to stone{/i} on every creature within 30 feet of it.\n{b}5 - Labyrinth{/b}. The vessel casts {i}maze{/i} on every creature within 30 feet of it.\n{b}6 - Nightmare{/b}. Shadowy tendrils reach out of the vessel and coalesce into 1d4 hostile shadow demons (see the MM for their stats), which appear in open spaces within 30 feet of it.\n{b}7 - Swarming Insects{/b}. The vessel casts {i}insect plague{/i}, centered on itself and with a radius of 30 feet.\n{b}8 - Unbridled Revel{/b}. The vessel casts {i}irresistible dance{/i} on every creature within 30 feet of it." compset="Wondrous">
