  <thing id="i5CMltBrnz" name="Molten Bronze Skin" description="This magical armor comes as a jug of molten bronze. The bronze adheres and contours to your skin when you attune to it. The armor can be worn under normal clothes without impeding bodily functions. Once you put it on, it can&apos;t be removed unless you choose to do so.\n\nWearing the armor grants you resistance to fire damage. The armor also doesn&apos;t impose disadvantage on Dexterity (Stealth) checks." compset="MagicArmor">
